{"tid":2219768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍絲闖港大毀連儂牆","createTime":"2020-09-27T06:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T06:36:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f125c72d415c99eaba754082d8c855790fe460d1","tid":2219768,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/KRZXF27HWNBCZBJ5ROZE2OMW2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FKRZXF27HWNBCZBJ5ROZE2OMW2Y%2F&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0uF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=26418720\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FKRZXF27HWNBCZBJ5ROZE2OMW2Y%2F&h=a55c023b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/KRZXF27HWNBCZBJ5ROZE2OMW2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藍絲闖港大毀連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一批中年男女昨晚闖入港大校園撕毀連儂牆，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QO1PtgtykpV_2nvxcgNgNzGjh1g=/3160x1881/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OSH34LNWDFDWTDAE2W7RY7OTJI.GIF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQO1PtgtykpV_2nvxcgNgNzGjh1g%3D%2F3160x1881%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOSH34LNWDFDWTDAE2W7RY7OTJI.GIF&h=dcea00ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大三幅連儂牆遭破壞，一名女子（左圖）撕文宣後大罵在場學生。港大校園電視影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保安無阻止<br />\n<br />\n根據網上片段，這批不明人士大多是中年男女，他們一邊搗亂，一邊高呼「我哋清理香港啲垃圾！清潔香港！」其間有人尖叫喝止，遭大叔以粗口辱罵並稱「你收聲啦！」眾人得手後往港鐵香港大學站方向離去，當時有多名港大保安在場，卻沒有阻止。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有人於「香江同心會」的藍絲專頁上載影片，炫耀清拆連儂牆戰績。片段所見，約10名男女到場撕毀連儂牆，短短不足30秒，已將三幅連儂牆上的文宣撕走。其間拍攝片段的女性語帶鄉音，自稱是「無大台、無機構、無錢攞」，更指出其行為是「喺度清潔香港大學」、「唔希望自己嘅仔女喺咁唔乾淨嘅大學入面讀書」。<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會表示，昨晚7時許，大批不明人士闖入港大校園範圍內，撕毀三幅連儂牆，又推倒學生會旗幟，其後離去；學生會稱將作進一步行動以示譴責。港大對事件深感遺憾，大學正檢視事件，不排除追究責任。"},{"pid":"e1d525dcb593239291d34f5362313dc505c6d6d3","tid":2219768,"uid":53922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"呢D人咪食飽飯無屎屙既廢閪囉。<br />\n香港多得呢班人唔少。"},{"pid":"a2c8c55f7bc2b053227e5996481fd36d56c8c290","tid":2219768,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"冇大學學位既垃圾去大學制做垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52ab1efc0bf5417f9b4e4e46b87ad7fd94f4b5c","tid":2219768,"uid":1358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"仲要啲食Q唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由佢地走<br />\n<br />\n有心放生"},{"pid":"a46afd22280d7e9e50431fefe9147a82334a0daf","tid":2219768,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c8c55f7bc2b053227e5996481fd36d56c8c290","tid":2219768,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"冇大學學位既垃圾去大學制做垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66552572937cba83b604fda1473c83e9473c347","tid":2219768,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"呢班廢人教出嚟嘅仔女入到大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中學畢業都有困難啦"}]}